betterquesting:10.desc:8: Craft an ME Interface! This item has two forms and you can swtich between them by placing one in a Crafting Table. They both function the same way, but one of them is a multiblock. This item can interface with the world: Try putting items in the top row, you'll be able to output from your ME System. Try putting Patterns there with a Crafting Card: You can automatically craft that item if you have a crafting CPU and some Molecular Assemblers, then output it in this Interface. You can also use it on machines, to input items either from a Pattern or by themselves. And finally, it's used in combination with Molecular Assemblers to automatically craft (see: Molecular Assembler part).
